import React, { Component } from 'react'; import './sdg16.css'; import '../../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css'; class Sdg16 extends Component { render() { return (

Goal 16: Peace, Justice and Strong Institutions

Promote peaceful and inclusive societies for sustainable development and providing access to justice for all people.

To reduce all forms of violence and the related death rates everywhere.

End exploitation, abuse, torture, trafficking and all forms of violence against children.

Providing legal identity for all people, including birth registration.

Strengthening relevant national institutions, including through international cooperation, for building capacity at all levels, in particular in developing countries, to prevent violence and combat terrorism and crime.

Promoting and enforcing non-discriminatory rules and policies.

To significantly reduce corruption and bribery in all forms.

To significantly reduce illegal financial and weapons flows, strengthen the recovery and return of stolen assets and combat all forms of organised crime.

To develop effective, transparent and accountable institutions at all levels to reduce corruption and crime,

Strengthening the participation of developing countries in the institutions of global governance.

To support the establishment and re-enforcement of legal systems and norms based on rule of law, independent judicial, reliable, and accountable institutions, free and fair elections and universal access to justice.

Ensuring public access to information and protect fundamental freedoms, in accordance with national legislation and international agreements.

 ); } } export default Sdg16;
